race.comment: LUCKY CHANCE (2) resumed over a mile at Bairnsdale beaten 1.5L. Is still shy of his best and the extra journey plays into his hands. He looks tough to beat in a very winnable race. HAIIRO (5) has been in the money at both runs with the latest at Avoca over 1860m. Fitter again and is close to a win. Ryan is a positive jockey engagement. HONEYJOY (3) is third-up and will be better for the outing here when stepping up to this trip. This isn't hard and he deserves consideration. JANEY BOPPER (6) came from well back to find a place at Avoca over 1860 at big odds. She won't be far away building on that.
